---

<Layout
  title="Mobil bilrengoring hos dig"
  description="Ny WashMax forside i Astro med video hero, SteamRex-inspireret brand og modelvaelger, tydelige pakker, daekningsomrade og hurtig vej til booking.">
  <main class="px-4 pb-10 sm:px-6">
    <section class="-mx-4 sm:-mx-6">
      <div class="relative min-h-[calc(100vh-7rem)] overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-visible bg-[#071611]">
        <video
          autoplay
          muted
          loop
          playsinline
          preload="metadata"
          class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
        >
          <source src={heroVideo} type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(3,9,8,0.82)_0%,rgba(5,17,13,0.58)_48%,rgba(7,21,17,0.34)_100%)]"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_78%_26%,rgba(101,214,250,0.26),transparent_20rem)]"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-40 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,transparent,rgba(3,9,8,0.38),rgba(3,9,8,0.72))]"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto flex min-h-[calc(100vh-7rem)] max-w-7xl items-center px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
          <div class="grid w-full gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.08fr_0.92fr] lg:items-center">
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#61c8f4]">
                Bilrengoring hos dig
              </p>
              <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-2xl font-display text-[clamp(3.2rem,8vw,6.3rem)] font-semibold leading-[0.92] tracking-[-0.05em] text-white">
                Fa helt ren bil med et klik
              </h1>
              <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-white/78">
                Nu med video hero og direkte modelvalg i toppen. Vaelg maerke,
                vaelg model og send kunden hurtigere videre til booking.
              </p>

              <div class="relative z-30 mt-10 max-w-4xl overflow-visible rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/12 bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] p-4 shadow-[0_24px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.22)] backdrop-blur-md">
                <div class="grid gap-3 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_auto]">
                  <div class="relative z-40 block" data-brand-combobox>
                    <span class="sr-only">Vaelg maerke</span>
                    <input
                      type="hidden"
                      data-brand-select
                      value={defaultBrand}
                    />
                    <button
                      type="button"
                      data-brand-trigger
                      aria-haspopup="listbox"
                      aria-expanded="false"
                      class="flex h-16 w-full items-center justify-between rounded-[1.1rem] border border-white/10 bg-white px-5 text-left text-lg font-medium text-[#10211a] shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.35)] outline-none transition hover:border-[#63bfe8] focus:border-[#63bfe8]"
                    >
                      <span class="flex min-w-0 items-center gap-3">
                        <span
                          data-brand-trigger-logo
                          class="flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-black/8 bg-[#f6f7f8] text-sm font-semibold text-[#10211a]"
                        >
                          {getBrandInitials(defaultBrand)}
                        </span>
                        <span data-brand-trigger-label class="truncate">
                          {getBrandLabel(defaultBrand)}
                        </span>
                      </span>
                      <span class="pointer-events-none flex items-center text-[#52b8e4]">
                        <Icon name="bx:chevron-down" class="h-7 w-7" />
                      </span>
                    </button>
                    <div
                      data-brand-menu
                      class="absolute left-0 right-0 top-[calc(100%+0.5rem)] z-[140] hidden overflow-hidden rounded-[1.3rem] border border-black/8 bg-white shadow-[0_24px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.22)]"
                    >
                      <div class="max-h-[22rem] overflow-y-auto py-3">
                        <p class="px-4 pb-2 text-sm text-[#7b8790]">
                          Populaere biler
                        </p>
                        {
                          popularBrands.map((brand) => (
                            <button
                              type="button"
                              data-brand-option={brand}
                              aria-selected={brand === defaultBrand ? "true" : "false"}
                              class:list={[
                                "flex w-full items-center gap-4 px-4 py-3 text-left transition hover:bg-[#f5f8fa]",
                                brand === defaultBrand && "bg-[#f5f8fa]",
                              ]}>
                              <span class="flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-black/8 bg-[#f6f7f8] text-sm font-semibold text-[#10211a]">
                                {
                                  getBrandLogo(brand) ? (
                                    <img
                                      src={getBrandLogo(brand)}
                                      alt={`${getBrandLabel(brand)} logo`}
                                      class="h-6 w-6 object-contain"
                                      loading="lazy"
                                      decoding="async"
                                    />
                                  ) : (
                                    getBrandInitials(brand)
                                  )
                                }
                              </span>
                              <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#10211a]">
                                {getBrandLabel(brand)}
                              </span>
                            </button>
                          ))
                        }
                        {
                          otherBrands.length > 0 && (
                            <>
                              <div class="mx-4 my-2 border-t border-black/6"></div>
                              <p class="px-4 pb-2 pt-1 text-sm text-[#7b8790]">
                                Alle biler
                              </p>
                              {
                                otherBrands.map((brand) => (
                                  <button
                                    type="button"
                                    data-brand-option={brand}
                                    aria-selected="false"
                                    class="flex w-full items-center gap-4 px-4 py-3 text-left transition hover:bg-[#f5f8fa]">
                                    <span class="flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-black/8 bg-[#f6f7f8] text-sm font-semibold text-[#10211a]">
                                      {
                                        getBrandLogo(brand) ? (
                                          <img
                                            src={getBrandLogo(brand)}
                                            alt={`${getBrandLabel(brand)} logo`}
                                            class="h-6 w-6 object-contain"
                                            loading="lazy"
                                            decoding="async"
                                          />
                                        ) : (
                                          getBrandInitials(brand)
                                        )
                                      }
                                    </span>
                                    <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#10211a]">
                                      {getBrandLabel(brand)}
                                    </span>
                                  </button>
                                ))
                              }
                            </>
                          )
                        }
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <label class="relative block">
                    <span class="sr-only">Vaelg model</span>
                    <select
                      data-model-select
                      class="h-16 w-full appearance-none rounded-[1.1rem] border border-white/10 bg-white px-5 pr-14 text-lg font-medium text-[#10211a] shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.35)] outline-none transition focus:border-[#63bfe8]"
                    >
                      <option value="" selected>Vaelg model</option>
                      {
                        defaultModels.map((model) => (
                          <option value={model}>{model}</option>
                        ))
                      }
                    </select>
                    <span class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 right-5 flex items-center text-[#52b8e4]">
                      <Icon name="bx:chevron-down" class="h-7 w-7" />
                    </span>
                  </label>

                  <a
                    href={bookingUrl}
                    data-hero-book
                    class="inline-flex h-16 items-center justify-center rounded-[1.1rem] bg-[#5ec1eb] px-8 text-lg font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#4bb8e6] lg:min-w-[11rem]"
                  >
                    Se din pris
                  </a>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-3 flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-white/86 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
                  <p>
                    Vaelg rengoring af hele bilen og spar minimum 398 kr. inkl.
                    gratis voksbehandling.
                  </p>
                  <p data-hero-selection class="text-white/72">
                    Audi valgt. Vaelg model for at fortsaette.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <div class="rounded-full border border-white/12 bg-white/8 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
                  Alle ugens dage kl. 08-17
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-full border border-white/12 bg-white/8 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
                  Dækker det meste af Sjaelland
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-full border border-white/12 bg-white/8 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
                  Miljoevenlig dampbehandling
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hidden items-center justify-end lg:flex">
              <div class="relative flex h-[20rem] w-[20rem] items-center justify-center rounded-full border-[10px] border-white/90 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_40%_30%,#a5ea5e,#7acb34_55%,#5ca61f_100%)] p-8 text-center text-white shadow-[0_28px_70px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]">
                <div class="absolute inset-[0.8rem] rounded-full border border-white/70"></div>
                <div class="absolute inset-[1.6rem] rounded-full border border-white/25"></div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                  <p class="text-[0.7rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-white/80">
                    Bestil komplet bilrengoring
                  </p>
                  <p class="mt-4 font-display text-[3.2rem] font-semibold leading-none">
                    Fa gratis
                  </p>
                  <p class="mt-2 font-display text-[2.4rem] font-semibold leading-[1.02]">
                    voksbehandling
                  </p>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight">
                    &amp; hel bils rabat
                  </p>
                  <p class="mt-5 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/84">
                    Spar minimum
                  </p>
                  <p class="mt-2 font-display text-[3.8rem] font-semibold leading-none">
                    398,-
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-7xl" id="pakker">
      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.78fr_1.22fr] lg:items-start">
        <div class="section-shell px-6 py-8 sm:px-8">
          <span class="eyebrow">Se din pris</span>
          <h2 class="mt-5 section-title">
            Frontpage-preview som leder direkte til booking.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-5 support-copy">
            SteamRex bruger et tydeligt pris- og valgflow helt oppe i heroen.
            Her starter vi med en enklere Astro-version for WashMax: brugeren
            ser biltype, pris og varighed med det samme, og klikker derefter
            videre til den eksisterende booking.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 grid gap-3">
            {
              benefits.map((item) => (
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-[1.25rem] border border-[var(--line)] bg-white/78 px-4 py-3">
                  <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgba(25,175,132,0.16)] text-[var(--brand-deep)]">
                    <Icon name="bx:bxs-check-circle" class="h-4 w-4" />
                  </span>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-[var(--ink)]">{item}</p>
                </div>
              ))
            }
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section-shell overflow-hidden px-6 py-8 sm:px-8">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--muted)]">
                Bilstorrelse
              </p>
              <h2 class="mt-2 font-display text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
                Vaelg din biltype
              </h2>
            </div>
            <p class="max-w-sm text-sm text-[var(--muted)]">
              De her priser kommer fra din nuvaerende WashMax struktur og er sat
              op som et skarpt preview, sa forsiden konverterer bedre.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
            {
              packagePreview.map((item, index) => (
                <button
                  type="button"
                  data-package-button={item.id}
                  class:list={[
                    "rounded-[1.4rem] border px-4 py-4 text-left transition duration-200",
                    index === 0
